    "title": "Breakdown",
    "description": "No matter which way you look at it, the larger blob is gently saying to the smaller disconnected one:\n&quot;It's not what YOU do, it's about what I do when you're not there...&quot;\n\nThe caption on the bottom reads:\n&quot;HARRY TOOK THE BREAKUP HARD, THOUGH RHONDA REALLY WAS AS NICE AS POSSIBLE, GIVEN THE CIRCUMSTANCES AND SUCH&quot;\n\nAnd the caption on the top reads:\n&quot;A GENE REGULATORY NETWORK CLEARLY EXPLAINS THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN THE TERMS &quot;LOSS-OF-FUNCTION PHENOTYPE&quot; AND &quot;GENE FUNCTION&quot;\n\nDo you get it?\n",
